Ability to edit via Markdown and formatting toolbar at the righthand side of the screen


Headings
'# The largest heading'
# The largest heading
'## The second largest heading'
## The second largest heading
'###### The smallest heading'
###### The smallest heading

Text Formatting
** ** or  __ __	: BOLD
* * or _ _ : Italic
~~ ~~	: Strikethough	

Quotes
> : Quote text
#note will indent
'': quote code
''' ''': quote large chunk code

Links
[text](https://blahblah.com/): weblink

Lists

To order lists simply add  number in front of list items
* : Bullets
1,2,3 : Ordered
- : Dash

If you would like to create a hierarchy, TAB

New Paragraph

Just leave a blank line
